# 產生曲線圖

```py
#!/usr/bin/python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np

f=open("./test.data","r")
lines=f.readlines()
result=[]
for x in lines:
    result.append(x.split(' ')[1])
f.close()


print result
plt.plot(result)
plt.legend(['Normal'])
plt.show()
```
